        <abstract> 
<p>Has "given the slip" to <hi rend="italic">Nepenthes</hi>, but is setting a plant up in an enclosure for special observation.</p>  
<p>Has some splendid <hi rend="italic">Sarracenia</hi> and will perform any miracle regarding them CD puts him up to.</p>  
<p>Charmed with CD’s account of <hi rend="italic">Pinguicula</hi>. Would like to try whether <hi rend="italic">Lychnis</hi> has the same use of viscid fluid.</p>  
<p>Has written for English <hi rend="italic">Utricularia</hi> for CD.</p> 
